cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object detection and pose estimation, specifically for cars in a scene. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and control, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The use of appearance randomization to generate synthetic data involves machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves designing synthetic content, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves geometric and photometric consistency, which could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics).
